items.name: QuollEyeTree
items.description: "QuollEyeTree" is a Cocoa File Management application for Mac OS X. It requires v10.6 Snow Leopard or later.  QuollEyeTree is inspired by XTree (and its successor ZTreeWin for Windows), but rather than trying to duplicate either, aims to implement the essential functionality, while retaining the Mac look and feel, and honouring the Apple Human Interface Guidelines.
